{
  "stem": "24409.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this didn't go back to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They arrived at the railroad station and sent home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- parents were horrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As soon as they left, they showed they were already in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And their children came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were again now probably more than before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had arranged for a ship to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And but the ship left them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They couldn't reorganize it so fast in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The ship left 3/4 empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I took the 50 people in who had come from the border countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I've already bring some out and show that we did not dare the undertaking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the word had gotten around in southern France and in Italy that you can get illegally to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There are people assembled in the ports.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We took them all up without money and Draga left with about 150.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was very few people for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And landed without any problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We landed on Yom Kippur, on Erev Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this is another 120 or 150.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I do not know the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In my book is the number that are saved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Draga had orders immediately to return now to Galatz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because we had arranged in the meanwhile, the people in Vienna had arranged, for transit visas through Romania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And Jabotinsky had some connection with Romania.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is through Romania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then they could then leave via Galatz to-- but they didn't-- It comes to my mind they didn't have the transit visas through Romania.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This man, Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Diamand, was a member of the Revisionist Party, a scientist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He told us, if you have trouble with transit visas, you don't need transit visas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They can all go on the Danube.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The Danube is by international agreement.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
